    <string name="AyudaText">
        Pappstillero\r\n
       User Instructions\r\n\r\n

Create Medicine\r\n\r\n
1º You must create the medicines, go to the top-right menu, and click on "New Medicine".\r\n
2º Fill the gaps, and put a medicine photo.\r\n
3º Save it.\r\n\r\n


Create Alarm\r\n\r\n
1º Click on the medicine you want to add the alarm.\r\n
2º When you are on the medicine screen, click, top-right menu, click on "New Alarm".\r\n
3º Fill the gaps - days, hours, and notes if necessary -.\r\n
4º Save the alarm\r\n\r\n


Delete Medicine\r\n\r\n
1º Select the medicine you want to delete.\r\n
2º Top-right menu, click on "Delete".\r\n\r\n

Add patient and carer data\r\n\r\n
1º Top-right menu, click on Menu superior derecho, pulsar sobre la opción "Patient-Carer data". \r\n
2º Top-right menu,edit.\r\n
3º Fill the gaps, and save it.\r\n\r\n

Edit or modify patient and carer data\r\n\r\n
1º To delete data, click on Delete, on top-right menu.\r\n
2º To modify data, click on Edit, on top-right menu.\r\n\r\n
